Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:38.24,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:41.77,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遥か彼方、僕らを待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:47.16,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ見ぬ未来へと‥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:56.54,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Always　 醒めきってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:59.71,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}速すぎる  Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:02.83,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明な闇に囲まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:06.32,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も似た網の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.53,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Found you  あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.77,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れ動いたPassion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.20,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my past
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:19.19,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全てキミに会うためのProcessだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:22.14,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
