Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:28.64,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:32.57,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}鼓動奮わせて居たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.42,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:39.92,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.26,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光の中  目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.98,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてくれたキミとなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.23,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.40,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.88,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.35,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷さえいま誇りになる
