Comment: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------OPCHNlrc----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:34.79,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去往不断延展的天边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:38.24,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明的翅膀将我引领
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:41.77,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}它在远方静待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:47.16,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飞往未曾预见的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:56.54,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理智清醒时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:59.71,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}时常感到日夜流逝过快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:02.83,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}四周被透明的黑暗包围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:06.32,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们都活在寸步难移的网中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.53,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寻觅你  每当风吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.77,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中激情仿佛随风跃动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.20,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:19.19,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一切皆为与你相会的前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:22.14,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:24.76,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}within the blackness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:28.64,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}远方传来的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:32.57,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让我不禁加快心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.42,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:39.92,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.26,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光辉洒下  我逐渐苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.98,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要你我互信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.23,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.40,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.88,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼前景色将焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.35,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昔日伤痕亦成今日荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:03:01.00,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因此与你一起超越重力的束缚
